cofh.lib.gui.element

Class ElementBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • cofh.lib.gui.element.ElementBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElementButtonBase, ElementDualScaled, ElementEnergyStored, ElementFluid, ElementFluidTank, ElementIcon, ElementListBox, ElementSimple, ElementSimpleBox, ElementSimpleToolTip, ElementSlider, ElementTextField, TabBase

    public abstract class ElementBase
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for a modular GUI element. Has self-contained rendering methods and a link back to the GuiBase it is a part of.
